{"tid":1645408,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係叫大家當手足／義士condom，但可唔可以唔好完全focus哂做偵探？","createTime":"2019-10-11T01:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T01:47:17.000Z","uid":179859,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ad74d67963560e80e53a2bdafd77159f249357","tid":1645408,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:18:41.000Z","msg":"利申先：唔係FC撚亦唔係想叫大家當可能被殺害(希望唔好係)嘅手足condom<br />\n只係想大家哂兩分鐘聽我鳩up兩句 諗下我講嘅野會唔會有少少道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由發生左幾單浮屍案開始<br />\n各門各派就開始眾說紛紜<br />\n十個人有十個講法<br />\n有人話係手足被拘捕後被狗強姦／輪姦後殺害<br />\n之後棄屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">論點</span>：有人影到一堆狗係發現屍體前夕係發現屍體地方出現／黑衫黑褲／後生etc<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">目的</span>：殺害&ldquo;唔聽話&rdquo;嘅人，港共學哂中共殺害異見人士唔洗解釋太多啦下話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人話係大陸運d屍體黎香港棄<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">論點</span>：咁多單極可疑嘅「屍體發現案」竟然得一單有&ldquo;家屬&rdquo;出黎 仲要不停話唔關「反送中」事。再者，即使將死者家屬全部軟禁又好點都好，總無可能將每一個義士身邊家人、親戚、朋友、同事每一個都捉哂／殺哂掛，點可以無一個人出黎講野？（除左今次15歲女手足呢單）我唔相信每個義士都無返三兩個好close關係嘅人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">目的</span>：「白色恐怖」嚇鳩d手足 令到佢地覺得男嘅就被虐待、打斷手腳之後殺害／女嘅就性侮辱，嚴峻d就強姦輪姦再殺害，最後棄屍。<br />\n終極目標係嚇到無人敢出黎protest。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我喺呢到唔係想講我覺得邊個啱邊個錯<br />\n因為除左死者，除左有份「經手」、有份策劃嘅衰人之外<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無人會知呀！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出面有手足話不如眾籌一大舊錢<br />\n叫有份做嘅黑警篤灰<br />\n之後比舊錢佢過世<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然我明個手足出發點係好 想幫女手足<br />\n但呢個根本上極難<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><em><strong>「香港警察」</strong></em></span>依家係香港黑社會最大嘅字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有睇過任何黑社會片都知<br />\n你去「做野」點會有機會比你留低篤灰嘅證據？<br />\n更何況係「龍頭大佬」？<br />\n一早收鳩哂你d相機電話<br />\n仲等你棄屍自個拍打個卡，影低其他同黨去<span style=\"color: orange;\">勒索</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">揸春袋</span>咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使有狗仲有丁點良心 (我覺得佢地就無鳩哂好耐)<br />\n肯企出黎指證其他狗／高級狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>都無用呀！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為佢地無可能有證據呀！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n亦正正因為係咁<br />\n我地先唔可以比我地嘅憤怒，疑惑，同埋成頭嘅問號 令到我地忘記哂<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">我地仲有好多野做</span></strong></span><br />\n頭先係連登cap左張熱門post圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mi6s6ET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMi6s6ET.jpg&h=96cb0dd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一個行動post都無？</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔係叫大家唔理有機會被棄屍嘅15歲女義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而係要兩樣同野做！</span></strong></span><br />\n戰線唔只一條<br />\n喺做偵探，查案嘅同時<br />\n唔可以坐係屋企電腦面前<br />\n嗌住sir this way等美國佬黎救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行動post呢？文宣呢？國際戰線呢？<br />\n<br />\n你問我<br />\n我就點都唔撚信堆狗係無辜嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係呢一刻<br />\n我地真係唔可以100％全情投入哂玩「誰是大兇手」呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要幾條戰線一齊打<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>我地要贏左呢場革命</strong></span><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先對得住 為我地擋子彈嘅手足<br />\n先對得住 為我地而死嘅義士呀！</span></span></em></strong><br />\n抖夠喇 <br />\n一齊加油啦好無？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n黑警死全家"},{"pid":"4030c9ac90b9977a1fbdb4dbc3cb93cb89e9ae24","tid":1645408,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:19:00.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"73a72736f52a175e3527d3becdcf2099dbe6c0c4","tid":1645408,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:19:11.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b6752da68eafc5b404b4740a2a58970953f9a4d4","tid":1645408,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"081657f8da2b31c40e640515346348f0ff0401c0","tid":1645408,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:19:33.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"81583a0a1e121db110dbe57e8142357c5fef3f4